{
  "title": "Xenial Flaky Greek Phyllo Baklava",
  "description": "A pungent and flaky Greek dessert featuring whole milk and shio-koji cure, friendly for those with egg allergies, formed into a baklava shape.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
  "diet": [
